ations for this bulk commodity plastic, e.g., for the\nproduction of electrocaloric devices for solid-state refrigeration which\nbenefit from a relaxor-ferroelectric-like response.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Jun 2017 09:38:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-27"}
